Package: gamedock
Architecture: amd64
Depends: ${shlibs:Depends}, ${misc:Depends}, waydroid, gamemode, mangohud
Description: An open-source Android gaming platform for Linux
 GameDock provides a seamless experience for running Android games on Linux
 through Waydroid, with features like automatic runtime management, controller
 support, game library organization, and system optimization.
 .
 Features include:
  * Automatic Waydroid installation and management
  * One-click APK, XAPK, APKS, APKM installation
  * Google Play Store integration
  * Game library with icons, metadata, and search
  * Controller support for Xbox, DualSense, Switch Pro, and more
  * GameMode and MangoHUD integration
  * Desktop launcher integration
